1.1.name: wordpress/jobs-finder
1.1.description: Plugin "Jobs Finder" gives visitors the opportunity to more than 1 million offer of employment. Jobs search for USA, UK, Canada, Australia. Jobs Finder are saved on our database, so you don't need to have space for all that information.
